company_name: COOP AGRICOLE DES PRODUCTEURS DE LA REGION DE FAYE SUR ARDIN
information: The company COOP AGRICOLE DES PRODUCTEURS DE LA REGION DE FAYE SUR ARDIN, founded in 1956, which operates in the Cereals and grains industry. It also operates in the Crop services industries. It is based in Faye Sur Ardin, France.
